  akshan: {"diff":"EVEN","tone":"#e8b84b","tldr":"Weather the poke — survive his Heroic Swing window and out-scale everything.","breakdown":"Akshan plays around Heroic Swing. Levels 1-5 are rent you pay; 6 starts the ramp, 11 ends the lane. E-poke his Heroic Swing gap and R any dive he greeds. Doran’s Shield blunts the poke war.","dos":["Farm safe to 6 / 11","E-poke when Heroic Swing is down","R the dive when he commits"],"donts":["Trade pre-6 for pride","Waste R on chip damage","Miss waves to dodge poke"],"key":{"slot":"E","name":"Heroic Swing","cd":"14s","note":"His dash + camera swing escape. Engage when it's down.","winT":"SWING DOWN","winS":"Scale, then E-melt with R cover."},"win":"Survive his Heroic Swing window and out-scale everything."},
